"Public application form for new artists. Submits name, email, bio, portfolio "
"URL and a personal statement to the community for review. Content is "
"rendered live on the frontend."
msgstr ""
"Fomu ya maombi ya umma kwa wasanii wapya. Hutuma jina, barua pepe, wasifu, "
"URL ya jalada la kazi na tamko binafsi kwa jamii kwa ajili ya ukaguzi. "
"Maudhui huonyeshwa moja kwa moja kwenye frontend."

#: blocks/join/editor.js:45
msgid ""
