"Email signup form for the public newsletter. A confirmation email is sent "
"before anyone is added to the send list (double opt-in). Content is rendered "
"live on the frontend."
msgstr ""
"Fomu ya kujisajili kwa barua pepe kwa jarida la umma. Barua pepe ya "
"uthibitisho hutumwa kabla ya mtu yeyote kuongezwa kwenye orodha ya kutuma "
"(uthibitishaji wa hatua mbili). Maudhui huonyeshwa moja kwa moja kwenye "
"upande wa mbele."

