"Small line identifying the artist whose subdomain is currently being viewed. "
"Renders nothing on the main Agnosis site."
msgstr ""
"Mstari mfupi unaomtambulisha msanii ambaye subdomain yake inatazamwa kwa "
"sasa. Hauchapi chochote kwenye tovuti kuu ya Agnosis."

