"Links to the current artist's own subdomain home. Renders nothing off an "
"artist subdomain."
msgstr ""
"Huunganisha kwenye ukurasa wa nyumbani wa subdomain ya msanii wa sasa. "
"Hauchapi chochote nje ya subdomain ya msanii."

#: blocks/breadcrumb-icon-link/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Breadcrumb Icon Link"
msgstr "Kiungo cha Ikoni ya Kipande cha Mkate"

#: blocks/breadcrumb-icon-link/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"A single icon-only link (Biography, Events, or a Contact popover) to/about "
"the current artist. Renders nothing if there's nothing to show (no biography/"
"events yet, or the artist has turned contact off), or off an artist "
"subdomain."
msgstr ""
"Kiungo kimoja chenye ikoni pekee (Wasifu, Matukio, au popo ya Mawasiliano) "
"kwa/kuhusu msanii wa sasa. Hauchapi chochote ikiwa hakuna cha kuonyesha "
"(bado hakuna wasifu/matukio, au msanii amezima mawasiliano), au nje ya "
"subdomain ya msanii."

