msgid "Newsletter Popover"
msgstr "Popo la Jarida"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter "
"signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer "
"template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled "
"(Settings → Newsletter)."
msgstr ""
"Kitufe cha ikoni kinachofungua popo la ukurasa mzima lenye fomu ya "
"kujisajili kwa jarida. Kinafanya kazi kivyake — kiweke moja kwa moja kwenye "
"sehemu ya kichwa au kiolezo cha sehemu ya chini; hakinachi chochote jarida "
"la umma likiwa limezimwa (Mipangilio → Jarida)."

